ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend the course for those interested in the time period or in social movements in general.
Yes, because it's a great introduction to and study of the very important social trends which swept the globe in the late 1960s.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course provided great insight into historical analysis and methodology which was especially helpful for those of us who were not historians.
The course fulfilled my international history requirement. It wasn't directly related to my political economy concentration, but I appreciated taking it for intellectual reasons.
